data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home. No detail has been overlooked in this thoughtful residence, from the kitchen granite countertops & SS appliances ensuring a move-in-ready experience. From the moment you step inside, the tile flooring guides you through a space that seamlessly combines elegance with practicality. Also can not forget about the brand new roof (2020), new HVAC system (2022), new water heater (2021). This home is a testament to thoughtful updates and timeless design, offering a comfortable retreat for those seeking a worry-free lifestyle. If this was not enough then the HUGE backyard where family gatherings, hosting, or even simple family time with the kids will be! So if this sounds like the home for you then book your private showing today before it is gone!
